Ramulus studies the figures as they come up, frowning in thought.

"I guess that's that," he says, "Any idea of how to counter the effects?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DeathScythe takes the container from the female bot and drains it, feeling 
the liquid go down his parched throat.

"How did I get so damaged?" he ask, looking over at the femm.
